            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Hmm it works for `nvim_put()` (and therefore `nvim_paste()`). Currently it passes an empty `regname`, but that may be mistaken for the unnamed register.\r\n\r\n> - `nvim_buf_set_text()`\r\n> - `nvim_buf_set_lines()`\r\n\r\nI don't think triggering `TextPut*` for these is desired. At least it's undesired for the use cases in #15136 and vim/vim#18171.",
